Current limitations:<br>
<ul class="bluebullets">
    <li>MorphML files are visualised "lines only"; i.e., diameters of sections or segments are not shown.</li>
<li>For NetworkML, only instance-based files can be mapped (lists of cells and connections), so no template based representations.</li>
</ul>


